    align:rationale "Both concepts refer to data used for AI system evaluation. The AIDOC definition is more specific regarding regulatory context ('before placing on the market'), while dpv-ai provides a broader description of testing data. They are highly similar but not interchangeable due to this difference in scope."^^xsd:string ;
